# News and discussions

1.  Darcs 2.1.0 released! With 20 bug fixes and 7 new features. Notable
    changes: darcs-2 repositories by default, HTTP robustness and better
    pending patch handling.
    -   [http://www.darcs.net/darcs-2.1.0.tar.gz](http://www.darcs.net/darcs-2.1.0.tar.gz)
    -   [http://lists.osuosl.org/pipermail/darcs-users/2008-October/014504.html](http://lists.osuosl.org/pipermail/darcs-users/2008-October/014504.html)

2.  Optimising darcs annotate. Darcs annotate is too slow. Proposed
    solution: create a cache mapping filenames to patches. Stay tuned
    for fast annotate in the future...
    -   [http://lists.osuosl.org/pipermail/darcs-users/2008-October/014371.html](http://lists.osuosl.org/pipermail/darcs-users/2008-October/014371.html)

3.  Eleven new contributors since darcs 2.0.2. Thanks, Alex, Florent,
    Gaetan, Judah, Matthias, Max, Nathaniel, Steve, Taylor, Thorkil, and
    Vlad!

